SUMMARY:Family Friendly Night Hike
DESCRIPTION:Join TLC to explore the wonders of Williamson Nature Preserve at night!\nAs dusk falls\, we’ll set out along the Two Pond and Pine Warbler Trails to investigate the sights and sounds of the forest after the sunset.  Participants will discover fun facts about our local nocturnal critters and explore how your senses adjust to navigating in the dark. \n \nThis is a free\, family-friendly event\, but preregistration is required. \n \nIf registration is full\, please fill out the waitlist form here by March 16th at noon. 
URL:https://triangleland.org/event/family-friendly-night-hike
LOCATION:Williamson Farm and Nature Preserve\, 4429 Old Country Mial Rd\, Raleigh\, 27610\, United States
ORGANIZER;CN="Amaya Horner":MAILTO:ahorner@triangleland.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
