SUMMARY:Trail Talks with TLC: Johnston Mill
DESCRIPTION:Get a special look at TLC's work on this staff led hike series!\nJoin TLC staff members on a moderate meander through Johnston Mill Nature Preserve. Learn about the history and special landmarks of this preserve as we also search the trails for spring wildflowers! This is a free event\, but preregistration is required.\n\n \n\n\n\nIf registration is full\, please fill out the waitlist form here by March 19th at noon.\n\nInclement Weather Policy: In the event of inclement weather\, you will be contacted by email for a call on cancellation or postponement.\n\n \n\n 
URL:https://triangleland.org/event/trail-talks-with-tlc-johnston-mill
LOCATION:Johnston Mill Main Entrance\, 2713 Mt. Sinai Rd\, Chapel Hill\, NC\, 27514\, United States
CATEGORIES:Hike
ORGANIZER;CN="Amaya Horner":MAILTO:ahorner@triangleland.org
END:VEVENT
