SUMMARY:Welcome to Spring!
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a walk and talk to admire the plants of spring!\nTLC Trail Guides Shelley and Deborah will lead you on an exploration of Horton Grove Nature Preserve. This will be a 3-mile hike at a leisurely pace with stops along the way to make observations about your surroundings. You will experience a variety of habitats as you meander through upland oak-hickory forests\, native plant meadows\, and alongside creek beds. This is a free event\, but pre-registration is required. \n\n \n\n\n\nIf registration for this event is full\, please fill out the waitlist form here by March 18th at noon.\n\n \n\n 
URL:https://triangleland.org/event/welcome-to-spring
LOCATION:Horton Grove Nature Preserve\, 7360 Jock Rd\, Bahama\, NC\, 27503\, United States
ORGANIZER;CN="Amaya Horner":MAILTO:ahorner@triangleland.org
END:VEVENT
