SUMMARY:Birdsong and Blooms
DESCRIPTION:Join us to take in the spring beauty of White Pines Nature Preserve!\nJoin TLC Trail Guide Mary Abrams on a meander through White Pines Nature Preserve! The preserve will be filled with the songs of our resident birds and early migrators as we discover the first blooms of spring on the cool slopes of the Deep and Rocky Rivers. We will hike over hilly terrain for about 2 miles as we immerse ourselves in the pleasures of early spring. We recommend that you bring binoculars if you have them but will have a few to borrow if you don’t. This is a free event\, but registration is required.\n\n \n\n\n\n \n\nIf registration is full\, please fill out the waitlist form here by March 23rd at noon.
URL:https://triangleland.org/event/birdsong-and-blooms
LOCATION:White Pines Nature Preserve\, 548 S Rocky River Rd\, Sanford\, NC\, 27330\, United States
END:VEVENT
