SUMMARY:Fungal Foray at Horton Grove
DESCRIPTION:Join the Triangle Mycological Society for a Fungal Foray!\n We'll explore various habitats and cover fungus types throughout the preserve\, seeking to discover a diverse array of fungal species. Our findings will be documented in iNaturalist\, so we encourage you to download the mobile app if you wish to participate in this citizen science project. The fungal foray is open to all knowledge levels.  We'll gather at the main parking lot at Horton Grove to begin our adventure.  This is a free event\, but preregistration is required. \n\n\n\n \n\nIf registration is full\, please fill out the waitlist form here by March 26th at noon. 
URL:https://triangleland.org/event/fungal-foray-at-horton-grove
LOCATION:Horton Grove Nature Preserve\, 7360 Jock Rd\, Bahama\, NC\, 27503\, United States
ORGANIZER;CN="Amaya Horner":MAILTO:ahorner@triangleland.org
END:VEVENT
