SUMMARY:Moth Night
DESCRIPTION:Join TLC\, in partnership with Backyard Butterflies\, for a night of mothing! We'll gather around glowing sheets and UV lights to see what nighttime wonders flutter by. This event is perfect for all ages and experience levels — whether you're a seasoned moth lover or just curious to learn more. Become a citizen scientist by bringing a camera or smartphone\, sign up for a free iNaturalist account\, and upload your nighttime discoveries. This event is free\, but preregistration is required.\n\n \n\n If registration is full\, please fill out the waitlist form here by March 27th at noon.
URL:https://triangleland.org/event/moth-night
LOCATION:Brumley South Nature Preserve\, 3055 New Hope Church Rd\, Chapel Hill\, NC\, 27514\, United States
ORGANIZER;CN="Amaya Horner":MAILTO:ahorner@triangleland.org
END:VEVENT
