SUMMARY:Speed Hike at Johnston Mill
DESCRIPTION:Come join TLC for an invigorating speed hike to wake up your Saturday morning!\nThis hike is led by one of our wonderful Trail Guides and will have a goal pace of 20 minutes per mile for about 3 miles. Explore Johnston Mill and see what all you can find while keeping your heart healthy and socializing on trail. This is a free event\, but preregistration is required.\n\n\n\nIf registration is full\, please fill out the waitlist form here by April 23rd at noon.\n\n 
URL:https://triangleland.org/event/speed-hike-at-johnston-mill-5
LOCATION:Johnston Mill Main Entrance\, 2713 Mt. Sinai Rd\, Chapel Hill\, NC\, 27514\, United States
CATEGORIES:Excercise,Health,Hike,Social
ORGANIZER;CN="Amaya Horner":MAILTO:ahorner@triangleland.org
END:VEVENT
